Kenapa mebel pertengahan abad ini
begitu dekat ke lantai?

250
00:13:07,745 --> 00:13:11,499
- Tak ada yang perlu sembunyi di 1950-an?
- Dekat ke lantai, itu dia!

251
00:13:11,582 --> 00:13:13,876
Kita harus berpikir seperti bayi.

252
00:13:13,959 --> 00:13:16,086
Aku bayi. Aku tak punya pekerjaan.

253
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:18,714
Aku senang dibungkus
jaket bertudung merah.

254
00:13:18,798 --> 00:13:20,216
Dan saat aku sedih,

255
00:13:20,299 --> 00:13:22,384
aku suka menjadi tinggi.

256
00:13:22,468 --> 00:13:24,929
Ruthie senang memanjat!

257
00:13:27,848 --> 00:13:29,683
Sesuai dugaanku.

258
00:13:29,975 --> 00:13:32,978
Liur baru. Pasti Ruthie.

259
00:13:33,187 --> 00:13:34,188
Todd!

260
00:13:34,271 --> 00:13:36,023
KRIM KIBBLE

261
00:13:36,106 --> 00:13:38,275
DUDUK. DIAM. TIDUR.

262
00:13:38,943 --> 00:13:42,279
Jadi, aku jelas tak boleh
menikah dengannya, bukan?

263
00:13:42,363 --> 00:13:44,573
Menurut kalian aku harus bagaimana?

264
00:13:44,657 --> 00:13:45,741
Hei, berikan.

265
00:13:46,659 --> 00:13:49,578
"Minta Tn. Peanutbutter
mengajakmu ke taman,

266
00:13:49,662 --> 00:13:51,914
