287
00:14:41,881 --> 00:14:43,340
Tentu. Segera datang.

288
00:14:45,885 --> 00:14:47,678
Tentu minuman nanti sempurna.

289
00:14:48,012 --> 00:14:49,722
Karena dia sempurna.

290
00:14:49,805 --> 00:14:51,599
Lihat saja dia.

291
00:14:51,682 --> 00:14:54,977
Dan, lihat dia.

292
00:14:57,771 --> 00:15:01,400
Dan dia, seperti digambarkan
dalam karikatur ini.

293
00:15:01,525 --> 00:15:03,360
Ia suka tenis dan papan seluncur?

294
00:15:03,444 --> 00:15:06,238
Apa lagi yang dia sembunyikan dariku?

295
00:15:06,322 --> 00:15:09,825
Apakah aku penyebabnya?
Apakah aku tak cukup layak?

296
00:15:09,992 --> 00:15:11,952
KAU HEBAT!
DIA DIBATALKAN!

297
00:15:12,036 --> 00:15:14,455
Ya, bukan aku masalahnya.

298
00:15:14,538 --> 00:15:18,876
Bahkan, kenapa aku di rumahnya?

299
00:15:18,959 --> 00:15:19,793
YA. PERGI SAJA.

300
00:15:19,877 --> 00:15:20,753
Saatnya berkemas!

301
00:15:23,631 --> 00:15:27,843
Aku akan ke hotel mewah dan...

302
00:15:28,677 --> 00:15:33,766
aku akan minta kamar gratis
sebagai imbalan promosi di medsos.

303
00:15:33,849 --> 00:15:35,267
Mereka pasti tidak mau.

304
00:15:35,351 --> 00:15:38,020
Jadi, akan kubayar kamarnya
lalu kuulas jelek di daring.

305
00:15:38,103 --> 00:15:39,063
Aku harus pergi.

306
00:15:40,397 --> 00:15:41,815
ITU TADI KUCING?

307
00:15:44,026 --> 00:15:47,112
Tunggu. Kenapa aku yang pergi?

308
00:15:47,196 --> 00:15:49,031
Dia yang selingkuh.

309
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:56,622
Dia bisa tinggal di taman bermain anjing,
apa peduliku!

310
00:15:56,705 --> 00:15:57,581
USIR DIA!

311
00:16:00,542 --> 00:16:02,878
Tetapi kenapa aku ingin dia tinggal?

312
00:16:03,170 --> 00:16:05,589
Aku sangat bingung.

313
00:16:05,673 --> 00:16:07,007
SAAT BINGUNG, BERENDAM

314
00:16:07,091 --> 00:16:09,843
Ide bagus, t_chavez!

315
00:16:10,135 --> 00:16:11,261
Sama-sama.

316
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,805
Celaka!

317
00:16:23,941 --> 00:16:25,234
Pembuat boba,

318
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:26,944
buat boba?

319
00:16:30,239 --> 00:16:32,199
Mau ditambah krim kocok?

320
00:16:36,787 --> 00:16:39,331
Bagaimana hidup lepas dari alkohol?

321
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:40,708
Mustahil.

322
00:16:48,549 --> 00:16:49,842
Tak ada jalan keluar aman.

323
00:16:49,925 --> 00:16:51,719
Tunggu kalau mau. Aku lewat jendela.

324
00:16:51,802 --> 00:16:54,138
Bukan aku alasan kau ke Chicago?

325
00:16:54,221 --> 00:16:56,056
Bukan. Aku harus pergi.

326
00:16:56,140 --> 00:16:59,059
Pickles? Sayang?
Mungkin ada sedikit kerumitan.

327
00:16:59,143 --> 00:17:01,020
Berengsek.

328
00:17:02,021 --> 00:17:04,106
Aku tahu minuman favoritmu boba.

329
00:17:04,189 --> 00:17:06,025
Tetapi tempo hari kau bilang,

330
00:17:06,108 --> 00:17:08,360
"Krim kocok hal terbaik di dunia,"

331
00:17:08,444 --> 00:17:10,904
diikuti dengan, aku kutip langsung,

332
00:17:10,988 --> 00:17:13,866
"Jadi, jauhkan dariku!"

333
00:17:13,949 --> 00:17:15,868
Aku hanya ingin kembali ke sana.

334
00:17:20,581 --> 00:17:22,041
Ya.

335
00:17:22,124 --> 00:17:23,125
Jangan salah,

336
00:17:23,208 --> 00:17:26,545
aku suka mencari jalan tengah
dari dua sisi bertentangan.

337
00:17:26,628 --> 00:17:29,006
Di mana bayinya? Itu dia bayinya.

338
00:17:29,298 --> 00:17:31,800
Di mana bayinya? Sial. Di mana bayinya?

339
00:17:34,511 --> 00:17:37,014
Suara pecah? Aku paham nada itu.

340
00:17:37,097 --> 00:17:41,518
Aku segera datang dengan minumanmu
seperti yang kau suka.

341
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:47,775
Ini.

342
00:17:48,609 --> 00:17:51,070
- Kau tahu di AA dapat lencana?
- Tanpa salsa?

343
00:17:51,361 --> 00:17:52,321
Kupakai leluconnya.

344
00:17:52,404 --> 00:17:54,448
Tetapi lencana itu hal penting.

345
00:17:54,531 --> 00:17:55,824
Kau dicuci otak,

346
00:17:55,908 --> 00:17:57,701
dibuat merasa lencana itu penting.

347
00:17:57,785 --> 00:17:59,995
Saat aku dapat lencana dua bulanku,

348
00:18:01,205 --> 00:18:04,500
